{"tid":1395065,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"85 返唔返工嘅 都要入黎","createTime":"2019-08-01T15:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T14:42:45.000Z","uid":269084,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe1b92fb75adb00558674cc6bf6dfa149b2c6ea","tid":1395065,"uid":269084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:37:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">罷工唔係淨係唔返工！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n唔返工只係一種方式，你可以請假，可以病假，可以曠工，冇問題的，都係其中一種方式。<br />\n<br />\n但大家要搞清楚，咩野係罷工！！！<br />\n<br />\n罷工唔係只係停工，<span style=\"color: red;\">係癱瘓系統運作。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">乜野係癱瘓系統運作？</span><br />\n<br />\n最簡單嘅例子：巴士司機唔返工，公司搵第二個車長替你，咁你嘅唔返工就冇意義。當然你可以話，只要有足夠車長唔返工，就冇人揸車，係真嘅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果呢班車長，揸左架車出街，遇上不幸事故，成架車阻住條路，就令到好多人返唔到工，咁就係另一件事喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">明唔明？如你嘅工作可被取締，咁你就要靠唔返工，同埋要令身邊嘅人一齊唔返工。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果你嘅工作係一個累全家嘅崗位，咁你返工，跟住響工作情況下最大地影響系統運作，遠比你唔返工影響大，因為你確保左你嘅工作冇被其他人取締，仲要掌控住成個罷工情況！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">至於實際要點做，你地響自己嘅工作崗位，點樣玩死老闆，一定比我清楚啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算你唔返工，都可以幫手癱瘓其他系統㗎，所以唔好hea，出去做野！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，需要的話，緊跟司長呼籲，緊守工作崗位啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（返到公司咪係守住左個工作崗位囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"0270dc8193dcdaaa84a2d2abc2c021010dacb13a","tid":1395065,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69569fc71ecfc4380dad418763a7473ed8bb9ed","tid":1395065,"uid":269084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:52:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fd5aa1e976d898cfccdd2f3aae42eb27a360d99","tid":1395065,"uid":270571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:59:22.000Z","msg":"入黎我話你聽班小朋友其實最急要咩物資<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394947\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394947</a>"},{"pid":"24cab142bffdb137a710b0048ee9879aacb6d690","tid":1395065,"uid":269084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T21:27:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e39e2ba800ff10b0f75967f0def9254dfc48046","tid":1395065,"uid":291007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:39:48.000Z","msg":"唔係唔返工嘅應該都參加7區集會咩"},{"pid":"255ce7d6349d490b1e04f51ff84aecb74d1d8acd","tid":1395065,"uid":269084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e39e2ba800ff10b0f75967f0def9254dfc48046","tid":1395065,"uid":291007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:39:48.000Z","msg":"唔係唔返工嘅應該都參加7區集會咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"7區集會又得，其他不合作亦得"},{"pid":"46b86430ec0921cc934fbc1f9e7bfb94a6524592","tid":1395065,"uid":204808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:14:13.000Z","msg":"唔返"},{"pid":"56571c81d69a55a09522e5dd1b9e